description: Ziccum AB engages in the development and commercialization of patented spray drying technology, LaminarPace. The company is headquartered in Lund, Skane. The company went IPO on 2018-10-25. LaminarPace is a CE-marked instrument for drying small amounts of drug substances with low losses. Ziccum AB intends to use its LaminarPace technology to begin creating new versions of dry powder therapies.
name: Ziccum AB
